{"tid":2336401,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南極洲首次出現武漢肺炎，至少錄得36宗確診個案，病毒傳遍世界七大洲！","createTime":"2020-12-22T14:32:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T17:02:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a503d2838aa6b9cec7d306a99775a4ae9216fa03","tid":2336401,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:32:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566669-20201222.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566669-20201222.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpEwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=282f945c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566669-20201222.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0e1f5cc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566669-20201222.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n南極洲首次出現武漢肺炎，至少錄得36宗確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓郵報》報道，確診患者來自智利位於南極洲的軍事基地，目前已經回國接受治療。智利當局暫時未公布感染源頭，但當地傳媒報道，本月較早時，智利一艘海軍軍艦，曾為涉事南極洲基地補給，船上多名人員回國後確診。<br />\n<br />\n在南極洲設立基地和研究所的各國，隨即禁止外來人員到訪，並要求駐南極洲的人員，暫停與其他基地人員來往。<br />\n<br />\n南極洲原本是全球最後一片「淨土」，隨著今次出現確診，武漢肺炎已經傳遍世界七大洲。"},{"pid":"a90723011593ceaf06b405f20533ca9d07333e0d","tid":2336401,"uid":79563,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:33:35.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎下一個挑戰：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/03121521/ISS-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA%E7%AB%99-624x448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2F03121521%2FISS-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E7%25AB%2599-624x448.jpg&h=312ea3b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c6cc5f9e998254325e1398bb1226783bcb245cf","tid":2336401,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/